{"tid":1443171,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"冰製屎坑，有冇得諗???","createTime":"2019-08-11T07:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:01:47.000Z","uid":284284,"like":4,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8e209dcde5adfba966c6095f25a3628a398c96","tid":1443171,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DxGum8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DxGum8.jpg&h=b50d90d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信每個人屋企嘅屎坑都會遇到同一個問題<br />\n就係，唔小心整污糟咗屎板，但係清潔屎板又好嘔心<br />\n所以我發明咗一個偉大發明：冰製屎板3000！<br />\n<br />\n無論你個屎坑上面有幾污糟都唔緊要，因為用冰做嘅屎板<br />\n一經室溫融化，所有污糟野都會因為 冰溶化+地心吸力 經 引水道 流入 排水管 <br />\n出污泥而不染，污糟野一一流走，以後唔再需要洗廁所!<br />\n<br />\n香港每一個家庭每一日，冰格白白用咗幾多電量？<br />\n而我哋嘅冰格, 除咗空氣, 其實99%係乜都冇<br />\n如果我哋冰格嘅用電量, 係用嚟製造 冰製屎板3000, 係咪更加有貢獻呢??<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 有得諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 戇L鳩! 我屌你牙!"},{"pid":"ea99f05872a6f2f67725471103d41de67a7ac6a7","tid":1443171,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"頂唔到幾多個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0023f15d0433b22fdba77642e5e3cdbd33942291","tid":1443171,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea99f05872a6f2f67725471103d41de67a7ac6a7","tid":1443171,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"頂唔到幾多個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"用冰格嘅原理 24小時 雪住佢, 點會頂唔到?"},{"pid":"2f310bc7b5e172e6a55eb23397c4a09f4d20acca","tid":1443171,"uid":258456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"冬天會唔會凍到連屎都唔想屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdcaab197e37a735baf98e4aafbdf061f2a47c3",